		    <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp;  All Abilities - 
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game and press Circle, Circle, Circle, Circle, Square</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp;  Change Spyro's color to red (pause the game and enter the following) - 
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Up, Right, Down, Left, Up, Square, R1, R2, L1, L2, Up, Left, Down, Right, Up, Circle</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp;  Change Spyro's color to black (pause the game and enter the following) - 
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Up, Right, Down, Left, Up, Square, R1, R2, L1, L2, Up, Left, Down, Right, Up, Down</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp;  Change Spyro's color to pink (pause the game and enter the following) - 
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Up, Right, Down, Left, Up, Square, R1, R2, L1, L2, Up, Left, Down, Right, Up, Square</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp;  Change Spyro's color to green (pause the game and enter the following) - 
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Up, Right, Down, Left, Up, Square, R1, R2, L1, L2, Up, Left, Down, Right, Up, Triangle</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp;  Change Spyro's color to yellow (pause the game and enter the following) - 
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Up, Right, Down, Left, Up, Square, R1, R2, L1, L2, Up, Left, Down, Right, Up, Up</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp;  Change Spyro's color to blue (pause the game and enter the following) - 
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Up, Right, Down, Left, Up, Square, R1, R2, L1, L2, Up, Left, Down, Right, Up, X</font>&nbsp;<br>
